<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Help - Pahana Edu</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-200 via-white to-sky-400 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-30 z-0"
         style="background: url('https://www.toptal.com/designers/subtlepatterns/uploads/symphony.png') repeat;"></div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-xl bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-7">
            <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 rounded-full p-4 shadow mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-question-circle fa-2x text-sky-700"></i>
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-sky-800 drop-shadow-lg">Help & Guidelines</h1>
            <p class="text-md text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">How to use Pahana Edu efficiently</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-7 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-500"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i></span>
                <p class="ml-2">Login with your role credentials. <b>ADMIN</b> can manage users, <b>MANAGER/CASHIER</b> handle POS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-500"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></span>
                <p class="ml-2"><b>Customers:</b> Add/update customer profiles and units consumed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-500"><i class="fas fa-boxes"></i></span>
                <p class="ml-2"><b>Items:</b> Manage inventory and pricing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-500"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i></span>
                <p class="ml-2"><b>Billing:</b> Select customer, add items & quantities, print receipt.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-500"><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i></span>
                <p class="ml-2"><b>Reports:</b> (Manager/Admin) View daily sales totals by date.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="index.jsp" class="inline-block bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-5 rounded shadow transition-all duration-200">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-1"></i>Back to Login
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
